OL,3,CNHS Trust tells visitors to stay away
OL,4,Cas hospital grapples with norovirus
OL,6,FPortsmouth Hospitals University NHS
OL,7,FTrust is urging visitors to stay away
OL,8,Ffrom the Queen Alexandra Hospital
OL,9,Funtil further notice, as it grapples
OL,10,Fwith norovirus cases.
OL,12,FThe Cosham-based hospital is asking
OL,13,Fpeople to only attend if experiencing
OL,14,Fa medical emergency, in order to try
OL,15,Fand prevent the spread of the virus.
OL,17,FAccording to the NHS, norovirus is a
OL,18,Fwinter vomiting bug that can cause
OL,19,Fnausea, vomiting, or diarrhoea.
