OL,3,CNHS Trust tells visitors to stay away
OL,4,Cas hospital grapples with norovirus
OL,6,FAnyone who has had symptoms within the
OL,7,Fpast 48 hours are being asked to avoid
OL,8,Fvisiting the hospital, to help protect
OL,9,Fvulnerable patients and staff.
OL,11,FThe Trust has since released guidance
OL,12,Ffor anybody visiting the site.
OL,14,FPeople are being advised to wash their
OL,15,Fhands with soap and water regularly,
OL,16,Fwhen entering and exiting the wards
OL,17,Fand hospital.
