OL,3,CNHS Trust tells visitors to stay away
OL,4,Cas hospital grapples with norovirus
OL,6,FVisits are being limited to one
OL,7,Fdesignated friend or family member per
OL,8,Fpatient for one hour a day. These
OL,9,Fvisiting times will need to be
OL,10,Freserved by contacting the ward
OL,11,Fdirectly.
OL,13,FVisiting hours are from 10am to 2pm,
OL,14,Fand 5pm to 8pm, seven days a week.
OL,16,FThe Trust says these restrictions will
OL,17,Fnot apply under compassionate grounds
OL,18,Ffor patients who are end-of-life or
OL,19,Frequire additional support.
