OL,3,CNHS Trust tells visitors to stay away
OL,4,Cas hospital grapples with norovirus
OL,6,FNo changes have been made for visits
OL,7,Fto children or maternity wards.
OL,9,FAnn Thomas, Chief Nurse and Director
OL,10,Fof Infection, Prevention Control at
OL,11,FPortsmouth Hospitals University NHS
OL,12,FTrust said: "We are continuing to see
OL,13,Fhigh numbers of norovirus cases in our
OL,14,Fhospital setting and people are
OL,15,Fcontinuing to visit the hospital with
OL,16,Fnorovirus symptoms.
